comment.author: 13935339@N05
comment._content: P-47D serial 42-76235 assigned to the 379th Fighter Squadron, 362nd FG made a forced landing after engine failure two miles north of High Halden (AAF Station 411) on 22 June 1944; pilot LT Robert E. Kelso survived the crash.
